\trl machaira
\ref G04001003400030 G04002604700034 G04002605200016 G04002605200036 G04002605200040 G04002605500030 G04101404300032 G04101404700016 G04101404800024 G04202102400008 G04202203600046 G04202203800012 G04202204900026 G04202205200042 G04301801000010 G04301801100018 G04401200200014 G04401602700030 G04500803500042 G04501300400038 G04800601700012 G05800401200026 G05801103400012 G05801103700010 G06600600400052 G06601301000022 G06601301000030 G06601301400066 L06900301300060 L07102801800010 L07600102500050 L07700301200016 L07700400600030 L07701008500010 L07800500200050 L08100302200030 L08500100900026 L08500202500008 L08500204100012 L08500204200018
