\line Osborn, Noel D., and Howard A. Hatton. 1999. A Handbook on Exodus. New York: United Bible Societies.
\line Péter-Contesse, René, and John Ellington. 1990. A Handbook on Leviticus. New York: United Bible Societies.
\line Reiling, J., and J. L. Swellengrebel. 1971. A Handbook on The Gospel of Luke. New York: United Bible Societies.
\line Reyburn, William D. 1992. A Handbook on The Book of Job. New York: United Bible Societies.
\line ———. 1992. A Handbook on Lamentations. New York: United Bible Societies.
\line Reyburn, William D., and Euan McG. Fry. 1998. A Handbook on Genesis. New York: United Bible Societies.
\line Sheffer, Avigail. 1995. “Needlework and Sewing in Israel from Prehistoric Times to the Roman Period.” In Fortunate the Eyes That See: Essays in Honor of David Noel Freedman in Celebration of His Seventieth Birthday, pages 527-559. Edited by Astrid B. Beck, Andrew H. Bartelt, Paul R. Raabe, and Chris A. Franke. Grand Rapids: Eerdmans.
\line Scott, R. B. Y. 1965. Proverbs, Ecclesiastes (Anchor Bible, 18). New York: Doubleday.
\line Simpson, D. C. 1913. “Tobit.” In The Apocrypha and Pseudepigrapha of the Old Testament in English, Volume 1, pages 174-241. Edited by R. H. Charles. Oxford: Clarendon Press.
\line Sukenik, E. L. 1928. “The Account of David’s Capture of Jerusalem.” Journal of the Palestine Oriental Society 8:12-16.
\line de Waard, Jan. 1997. A Handbook on Isaiah. Winona Lake, Indiana: Eisenbrauns.
\line de Waard, Jan, and William A. Smalley. 1979. A Handbook on The Book of Amos. New York: United Bible Societies.
